82
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,320
And it's not a festival today.

83
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,360
What are you doing with it?

84
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,400
If it were a festival or something,

85
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,760
I couldn't bear to drink it.

86
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,040
I was going to save the liquor

87
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,200
