88
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,400
And great! The factory manager will enjoy it first.

89
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,280
So, you are also going to do this kind of stuff?

90
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:56,960
Zhiyuan.

91
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,640
Yes?

92
