102
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,040
How can we talk?

103
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,240
The shop is about to open.

104
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,800
You can't keep it a secret.

105
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,320
If Dad knows it until then,

106
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,920
