107
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,080
Okay, I see.

108
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,640
Just go home.

109
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,000
Otherwise, Mom will be worried.

110
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,480
Fine, I'll go first.

111
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,160
Just go.

112
