Mom! Mom!

114
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,120
Help me!

115
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,600
My dad is drunk again.

116
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:30,440
I told him not to drink too much.

117
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,520
Why is he drunk again?

118
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,600
Dad, we are home.

119
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:33,600
Take care.

120
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,000
I told you not to drink too much.

121
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,240
Why did you get so drunk?

122
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,080
Manager Xu drank like a fish.

123
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,680
Come here.

124
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,600
Let's go. Let's have dinner.

125
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:44,840
Come and have dinner.

126
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,600
I think

127
