128
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,320
Where's your brother?

129
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,680
My brother…

130
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:58,600
He said he would come back to have dinner later.

131
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,880
