132
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,520
It's so late.

133
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,040
Have your meal. I'll deliver some food to him.

134
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:04,520
Yeah.

135
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,040
Mom!

136
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,440
Let me deliver food to him.

137
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,160
Just eat your meal. I'll do it.

138
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,520
Don't do that!

139
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,160
We should feed dogs

140
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,240
