141
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,520
Have your meal.

142
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,240
Mom, Dad, we're back!

143
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,560
Welcome back.

144
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:33,000
Mom, did my letter arrive?

145
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,840
You ask this question every day!

146
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,080
You know what? Even the postman

147
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:39,160
goes around our house!

148
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:40,960
That's not okay.

149
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,960
Looks like I have to call Chen.

150
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,200
It's been a couple of days.

151
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,240
Don't trouble Chen all day, okay?

152
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,120
She's newly married and has a lot of things to do.

153
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,760
Wash your hands and have dinner.

154
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:52,040
How about this? When I pass the post office on my way to work tomorrow,

155
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,200
I'll ask somebody for you.

156
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,400
Hello.

157
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,760
Dad, it's for you.

158
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,560
Me?

159
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,920
Who's that?

160
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,280
It's an emergency case. I must go now.

161
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,760
Dad, I'm ready!

162
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,560
You'll go with me?

163
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,120
Let's go!

164
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,560
Vomiting and diarrhea, right?

165
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,400
When did this happen?

166
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,240
He's been like this since afternoon.

167
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,840
Will he be fine?

168
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,840
If something happens to him,

169
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,760
I can't live either.

170
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:33,120
Ma'am, my dad is an amazing doctor.

171
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,520
He can surely cure him.

172
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:38,960
It's fine.

173
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,240
No big deal.

174
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,910
I'll give you a prescription in a while.

175
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,120
Antidiarrheal

176
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,520
and medicine to protect the intestinal mucosa.

177
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,840
He'll be fine after taking medicine.

178
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,920
Huang, let's thank Dr. Tan.

179
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,680
You little bastard!

180
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,000
You really pissed me off!

181
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:29,680
You think I can't discipline you anymore?

182
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:32,200
Don't make me mad again!

183
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,440
Hello.

184
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,600
Diarrhea again?

185
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,200
What diarrhea?

186
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,840
Why did you take so long to answer the phone?

187
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:55,200
Tan, I beat Minghui.

188
00:09:57,360 --> 00:10:01,640
Four years of studying in Beijing has made this kid wild.

189
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,240
After graduation…

190
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,480
What's wrong with Dad?

191
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,160
He got drunk again.

192
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,160
And I took a couple of blows for you just now.

193
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,200
You got beaten?

194
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,960
Of course.

195
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,240
Where did you get beaten?

196
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,320
He spanked me.

197
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,400
What do you mean by "right"?

198
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,800
You told me not to beat kids, didn't you?

199
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:20,400
Why are you saying this is right now?

200
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,720
What are you talking about?

201
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:22,920
Tan?

202
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:24,720
Tan?

203
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:35,840
Answer the phone.

204
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,800
No, no.

205
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,600
It's either Qiang or Meng who would call me so late.

206
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,040
Let's sleep.

207
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:41,440
Wouldn't you answer it if it's for you?

208
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,440
No, no!

209
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,360
Yumei! Yumei!

210
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,480
Chen?

211
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,480
It's me, Gao!

212
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,720
Chen Jianguo!

213
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:05,040
Meng, what's wrong with you?

214
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,640
You always call me in the middle of the night!

215
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,200
Can't you just wait until tomorrow?

216
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,280
I just want to talk…

217
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:13,080
Hang up on me, huh?

218
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,600
You…

219
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,440
Meng,

220
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,480
my heart just thumps

221
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,840
when I hear the telephone ring.

222
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,280
Just stop calling!

223
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,600
And don't get drunk anymore!

224
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:36,280
Hello, I'll sleep right away, Ma'am.

225
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,800
Go to bed right now.

226
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,400
Hey, don't push me.

227
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,200
I haven't changed my shoes yet.

228
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,160
Minghui, go back to your room quickly.

229
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,360
Why are you up so early?

230
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,160
You still want to win the TV?

231
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,600
You just had to mention that, didn't you?

232
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,480
Have you seen Uncle Liu, the postman?

233
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,120
It's too early.

234
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,280
He's still far away from this area.

235
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,200
Tan Xin.

236
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:22,280
Why are you up so early too?

237
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,280
Put it on.

238
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,040
Minghui.

239
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,480
You have to deliver the goods, right?

240
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,400
Yeah.

241
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:31,280
And I need you to take care of the shop for me.

242
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,400
I'll be right back.

243
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,080
How's your bottom now?

244
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,040
Dad must have hit you hard.

245
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,280
Uncle Gao spanked you?

246
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,640
Good students like you

247
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,720
also got beaten at home?

248
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,240
It's none of your business.

249
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,320
